{"tid":672571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續向中國低頭 Apple 要求開發者移除 CallKit","createTime":"2018-05-21T06:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T07:32:49.000Z","uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"228a574367140c5a670f3da2534af53c9d274c10","tid":672571,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"中國對於國內手機應用向來諸多限制，Apple 為了打入這個市場，對於規例都相當服從，繼早前把 VPN 相關的 App 下架後，最近亦要求開發者移除 CallKit 方可以在中國區 App Store 上架。<br />\n<br />\n早前有開發者表示，收到 Apple 的通知，因為中國工業與信息產業部的規定，在中國 App Store 上架的 App 都不可以含有 CallKit 服務，如果想讓 App 在中國 App Store 上架，就要移除 CallKit。在中國以外的 App Store 則不受影響。<br />\n<br />\nApple 方面未有解釋為什麼不可以使用 CallKit，這個工具本身不是直接帶來通話服務，不過可以讓 App 在鎖機介面上顯示有如一般來電的接聽畫面。而同樣有類似使用方式的 FaceTime 在中國則不能使用。微信之前亦同樣有採用 CallKit，不過繼禁令實施之後已經移除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/20/apple-clamps-down-on-callkit-apps-in-china/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2Fapple-clamps-down-on-callkit-apps-in-china%2Fsoftware%2F&d=kmTCRgqU9%2FUFNKzfZ8RYgHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e921fdbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/20/apple-clamps-down-on-callkit-apps-in-china/software/</a>"},{"pid":"aa62e06359284d214d350889abc8ab9f43866df9","tid":672571,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"點解要禁?"},{"pid":"377a636bd0aca4783e363f53ab00db5d95613ebe","tid":672571,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a24827f003fefbfb5381f8fd999050e342c7d0be","tid":672571,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa62e06359284d214d350889abc8ab9f43866df9","tid":672571,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"點解要禁?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"可能支国套野只係識mon字<br />\n要做監聽要用返電話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8201c021660f3b41f091c0f0b10506d496589c4d","tid":672571,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}